{"tid":223803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[絲打入]谷m辛苦啲定嚟m辛苦啲？","createTime":"2017-04-30T14:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T14:01:12.000Z","uid":34337,"like":56,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94cc4173c76a977e6b39c8edec5971f453278c47","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：谷m<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嚟m<br />\n <br />\n利申：揀唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n谷m會波痛，下面唔舒服，個人又燥底<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚟m就痛到仆街，會作嘔，第一日完全食唔落野，基本上一放落口就想嘔，淨係可以飲野，呢幾個月試緊第1日嚟飲紅豆水，都叫有啲用，可以舒緩到，無痛得咁犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇下有無其它方法可以參考下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好同我講搞到我10個月唔嚟或者飲暖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4663338360a5442162022f0ca70de016cb47d0ed","tid":223803,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T14:59:43.000Z","msg":"我係雞"},{"pid":"40b8ec52da47ac8f1746ef7ebaa5a2b0f3865303","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係雞</blockquote><br />\n雞都會嚟m"},{"pid":"e32c91f77f0af8b0f6c81cad444c4e7b968e3aba","tid":223803,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係雞</blockquote><br />\n雞都會嚟m</blockquote><br />\n漏m最辛苦"},{"pid":"1e7a6bdd9fdbdaf74fc9f5f133c616e785e4b5fd","tid":223803,"uid":140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:01:10.000Z","msg":"男人老狗打j多有幻覺？"},{"pid":"407d4534afadbad5c35a7155b80115d96543bc75","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係雞</blockquote><br />\n雞都會嚟m</blockquote><br />\n漏m最辛苦</blockquote><br />\n我多數第一日嚟瞓覺會漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後都無乜"},{"pid":"fc8aad0c8545ae15c294a3c1b18883cff9611790","tid":223803,"uid":1621,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:04:26.000Z","msg":"成日覺得啲女人拎黎m放大黎講...<br />\n<br />\n借黎m放肆自己既情緒發脾氣"},{"pid":"347d8418a017286d926af5e765d134a02284853b","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得啲女人拎黎m放大黎講...<br />\n<br />\n借黎m放肆自己既情緒發脾氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我唔會幫曬女人嘅，因為我都有試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但嚟m又真係好辛苦嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebc1e6ad7015b77998a8501e39e531dc2497729","tid":223803,"uid":87395,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"谷m 最撚辛苦 皮膚差到想死 波波同腰又痛 個肚成日谷住谷住咁 有時又好似生蟲咁想食野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7086a91dea75649fc24f5a7c1e4affaa915debad","tid":223803,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"呵返"},{"pid":"654a8d2a64ab17efb379756d40faff14c696d84c","tid":223803,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:53:48.000Z","msg":"嚟緊嗰陣除左麻煩啲之外都無咩野，因為我好少會痛，係都只係少少似肚痛嘅感覺，忍一忍無野。但嚟之前個胸會好漲，督下都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日追巴士痛到忍唔住禁住佢跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b51e303672ea755a80e5957a554212a5951de5","tid":223803,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日覺得啲女人拎黎m放大黎講...<br />\n<br />\n借黎m放肆自己既情緒發脾氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚟m真係辛苦真係燥嘅<br />\n不過真係唔應該當自己攞正牌發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw有fd痛得好誇張面青口唇白，我自己就無咩感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46534b811be306b9688284315eb2106646c63c2b","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>谷m 最撚辛苦 皮膚差到想死 波波同腰又痛 個肚成日谷住谷住咁 有時又好似生蟲咁想食野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又無乜點爆瘡 個對波真係好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d503900261e6bba8f76137c6f7a79439f49e6b7b","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>谷m 最撚辛苦 皮膚差到想死 波波同腰又痛 個肚成日谷住谷住咁 有時又好似生蟲咁想食野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又無乜點爆瘡 <span style=\"color: red;\">但</span>對波真係好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"13ccee635c6ed5e9a511d23b63ebbc7a170c56a2","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呵返</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89c1bd6d20051e75a4c62b4045f499bc0bbc2a7","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚟緊嗰陣除左麻煩啲之外都無咩野，因為我好少會痛，係都只係少少似肚痛嘅感覺，忍一忍無野。但嚟之前個胸會好漲，督下都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尋日追巴士痛到忍唔住禁住佢跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好陰公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a752be9d725cf3776302ce884caf7e688ae97e5","tid":223803,"uid":34337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T16:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote